content.rendered:
Directed by A.L. Vijay.

Written by Paul Aaron. Chintan Gandhi.

Cast Rajiv Thakur(Sanjay) . Rj Ajay(Krishna’s Office Colleague). RJ Balaji(Cameo). Tamannaah Bhatia(Sweety). Prabhu Deva(Krishna Kumar (as Prabhudheva)). Chintan Gandhi(Krishna’s Office Colleague). Karishma Gulati(The Neighbor). Esha Gupta(Ruby / Special Apperance (Rail Gaddi)). Hema(Devi’s mother). Gurpreet Kaur(Krishna’s Office Colleague). Farah Khan(Farah). Ravi Khanna(Film Producer / Villain). R.V. Udhaya Kumar(Devi’s father). Joy Mathew(Krishna’s father). Nassar(The High Tech Tantrik). Omaar((as Omar)). Abijith Paul(Film Producer’s Son). Sapthagiri(Cameo). Murli Sharma(Raj Khanna’s PA). Kanwalpreet Singh(Krishna’s Office Colleague). Raju Sundaram(Cameo (Chal Maar song))

Language Hindi.

Producers Deepshika Deshmukh. Ajay Dhama. Rosita Fernandes. K. Ganesh. Ashwin Kumar. Omaar. Lawrence Paul. Abhishek Rao. Gautam Sachar. Sonali Sood. Sonu Sood. Muskaan Khan Thakur. Jitendra Yadav.

Production Prabhudheva Studios. Shakti Sagar Productions.
